{"tid":1778062,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"陳果新作《墮胎師》","createTime":"2019-12-10T15:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T11:44:53.000Z","uid":4260,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5ad9a3994e198c435775ae967a08b8c7fe60e3","tid":1778062,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mediafiles.cinema.com.hk/broadway/cmsimg/cinweb/movie/movie_1575971252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmediafiles.cinema.com.hk%2Fbroadway%2Fcmsimg%2Fcinweb%2Fmovie%2Fmovie_1575971252.jpg&h=7169fff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12月放映5場，未有預告片<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n<br />\n珍姐是家庭主婦，但最不可思議的卻是她還是一位黑市墮胎師，她的客人來自不同階層，有青年婦女，也有未成年少女。 <br />\n<br />\n剛滿十六歲的女兒Kiki向珍姐表態，希望到她十八歲時，珍姐可以將她擁有現住的房產改到Kiki名下。珍姐拒絕了，因為住屋在香港是民生最殘酷一環，寧與屋共存，不與親共眠是她的座右銘。不久，Kiki就離家出走，投靠長年住在深圳的離婚爸爸。 <br />\n<br />\n珍姐到學校找Kiki勸她回家，Kiki沒有理會。珍姐想到有一次，Kiki為了驅趕到家做墮胎的同齡女生，跟她吵了一場。珍姐說她是靠這個把Kiki養大成人，KiKi說這是在踐踏生命。於是珍姐不再做墮胎師，改行了，甚至還進了教會，為了女兒而改變。 <br />\n<br />\n一天，Kiki昏倒在街上。當她在醫院醒來時，她知道自己又回到珍姐身邊&hellip;&hellip;這是改編自真實故事，絕不荒誕，還看似理所當然。這也許也是你的故事，如有巧合，絕不奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n演員：白靈、伍詠詩、鄧月平、李玗蓁、鬼塚<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cinema.com.hk/tc/movie/details/12086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinema.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fmovie%2Fdetails%2F12086&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=d980f3e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cinema.com.hk/tc/movie/details/12086</a>"},{"pid":"4cddbe746b15b21bceb02948494d014d8ec91ac9","tid":1778062,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"[行動]和你踩！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778037</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74b57da944fa74425ad25f2736208a5f3ca5fd0c","tid":1778062,"uid":307619,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"鄧月平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla